\begin_inset Formula $S_{n}\left(t,\omega\right)=\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}B_{t_{j}^{\left(n\right)}}\left(\omega\right)1_{\left[t_{j}^{\left(n\right)},t_{j+1}^{\left(n\right)}\right)}\left(t\right)$
\end_inset

.
