\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Proof

\size largest
Let 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta B_{t_{j}^{\left(n\right)}}\coloneqq B_{t_{j+1}^{\left(n\right)}}-B_{t_{j}^{\left(n\right)}}$
