\begin_inset Formula $\Delta\left(B_{t_{j}^{\left(n\right)}}^{2}\right)=B_{t_{j+1}^{\left(n\right)}}^{2}-B_{t_{j}^{\left(n\right)}}^{2}$
\end_inset

.
