\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{0}^{t}B_{s}dB_{s}=\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}B_{t_{j}^{\left(n\right)}}\Delta B_{t_{j}^{\left(n\right)}}
\]

\end_inset

So we have to evaluate this limit.
