\]

\end_inset

and so 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}B_{t_{j}^{\left(n\right)}}\Delta B_{t_{j}^{\left(n\right)}}=\frac{1}{2}B_{t}^{2}-\frac{1}{2}t
